BEGIN
        FOR h in 0..23 LOOP
            MERGE INTO core_usage_summary t 
            USING (SELECT region, ad, category, pool_name, family, record_date, cores FROM core_usage_summary_v WHERE category is not null and record_date = TRUNC(sysdate-1) + (h/24) ) v 
            ON (t.region = v.region AND t.ad = v.ad AND t.category = v.category AND t.pool_name = v.pool_name AND t.family = v.family AND t.record_date = v.record_date )
            WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET t.cores = v.cores 
            WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
            INSERT (t.region, t.ad, t.category, t.pool_name, t.family, t.record_date, t.cores) 
            VALUES (v.region, v.ad, v.category, v.pool_name, v.family, v.record_date, v.cores);
            COMMIT;
        END LOOP;
        MERGE INTO core_usage_daily_summary t 
        USING (SELECT region, ad, category, pool_name, family, record_date, cores FROM core_usage_daily_summary_v WHERE category is not null and record_date = TRUNC(sysdate-1) ) v 
        ON (t.region = v.region AND t.ad = v.ad AND t.category = v.category AND t.pool_name = v.pool_name AND t.family = v.family AND t.record_date = v.record_date )
        WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET t.cores = v.cores 
        WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
        INSERT (t.region, t.ad, t.category, t.pool_name, t.family, t.record_date, t.cores) 
        VALUES (v.region, v.ad, v.category, v.pool_name, v.family, v.record_date, v.cores);
        COMMIT;
        MERGE INTO core_usage_weekly_summary t 
        USING (SELECT region, ad, category, pool_name, family, record_date, cores FROM core_usage_weekly_summary_v WHERE category is not null and record_date = TRUNC(sysdate-1, 'D') ) v
        ON (t.region = v.region AND t.ad = v.ad AND t.category = v.category AND t.pool_name = v.pool_name AND t.family = v.family AND t.record_date = v.record_date )
        WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET t.cores = v.cores 
        WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
        INSERT (t.region, t.ad, t.category, t.pool_name, t.family, t.record_date, t.cores) 
        VALUES (v.region, v.ad, v.category, v.pool_name, v.family, v.record_date, v.cores);
        COMMIT;
    END;

BEGIN
        insert into compute_tou_obusers_report 
        select tas_account_id, tenant_id, admin_email, 
               min(ooc_count) as min_ooc_daily_count, 
               round(avg(ooc_count)) as avg_ooc_daily_count, 
               max(ooc_count) as max_ooc_daily_count, 
               TRUNC(sysdate-1) as report_date
        from (
            select tas_account_id, tenant_id, admin_email, TRUNC(time_created) as date_created, sum(error_count) as ooc_count
            from dw_stg_user.compute_ooc_data
            join dw_stg_user.accounts using (tenant_id)
            where shape = 'VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro'
             and  time_created >= TRUNC(sysdate-1)
             and  time_created < TRUNC(sysdate)
             and  tas_state in ( 'ACTIVE', 'ALWAYS_FREE_ONLY')
             and  account_type = 'EXTERNAL'
            group by tas_account_id, tenant_id, admin_email, TRUNC(time_created)
        )
        group by tas_account_id, tenant_id, admin_email
        having max(ooc_count) >= 200;
        COMMIT;
    END;

insert into amd_history 
with dates as (
select trunc(sysdate-1)  as day from dual
)
select * from (
SELECT a.*,
       pool_category10,
       pool_category20,
       pool_category30
FROM (SELECT a.record_date,
             b.instance_state,
             b.capacity_state,
             b.capacity_category,
             b.super_category,
             a.region,
             a.ad,
             UPPER(SUBSTR(a.ad,-4)) AS generic_ad,
             a.pool_name,
             a.shape,
             a.hardware_shape,
             a.server_type,
             a.fault_domain,
             a.serial_no,
             common_name, 
             e.category, 
             SUM(a.cores) cores,
             SUM(CASE WHEN a.server_type = 'VMI' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS instance_count
      FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact a
        LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_state_dim b ON a.sub_state_key = b.sub_state_key
        LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compartment_dim d on a.compartment_id = d.compartment_id 
        LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.account_dim e on d.tenant_id = e.tenant_id 
      WHERE a.record_date = (select day from dates)
      GROUP BY a.record_date,
               b.instance_state,
               b.capacity_state,
               b.capacity_category,
               b.super_category,
               a.region,
               a.ad,
               SUBSTR(a.ad,-4),
               a.pool_name,
               a.shape,
               a.hardware_shape,
               a.server_type,
               a.fault_domain,
               a.serial_no, 
               common_name, 
               e.category) a
  LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_pool_dim b
               ON (COALESCE (LOWER (a.pool_name),'null_pools') = LOWER (b.pool_name)
              AND a.capacity_category = b.capacity_category
              AND a.super_category = b.super_category))
WHERE hardware_shape = 'BM.Standard.E2.64';

insert into daily_actuals_by_forecast_group  
SELECT trunc(sysdate) as record_date,
       region,
       fc_customer_name,
       b.generation,
       b.sku,
       usage_classification, 
       SUM(a.cores) cores
FROM DAILY_FORECAST_ACTUALS_VIEW a
  LEFT OUTER JOIN compute.compute_shape_detail_dim b ON a.hardware_shape = b.shape
GROUP BY trunc(sysdate),
         region,
         fc_customer_name,
         b.generation,
         b.sku,
         usage_classification;

insert into daily_hardware_consumption_rate
SELECT MAX(record_date) AS record_date,
       region,
       ad,
       hardware_shape,
       SUM(cores - d1) / 7 AS consumption_rate
FROM (SELECT a.*,
             cores - d1
      FROM (SELECT a.*,
                   LAG(cores,1) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date ASC) AS d1,
                   COUNT(record_date) OVER (PARTITION BY ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date ASC)-1 AS total_rows
            FROM (SELECT record_date,
                         region,
                         ad,
                         CASE
                           WHEN shape = 'VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro' THEN shape
                           ELSE hardware_shape
                         END AS hardware_shape,
                         SUM(average) AS cores
                  FROM dw_stg_user.COMPUTE_CAPACITY_DAILY_COMPARTMENT_USAGE
                  WHERE pool_category10 = 'Usage'
                  AND   record_date IN (SELECT record_date
                                        FROM (SELECT a.*,
                                                     RANK() OVER (ORDER BY record_date DESC) r
                                              FROM (SELECT DISTINCT record_date
                                                    FROM dw_stg_user.COMPUTE_CAPACITY_DAILY_COMPARTMENT_USAGE
                                                    WHERE record_date >SYSDATE -12) a)
                                        WHERE r < 9)
                  GROUP BY record_date,
                           ad,
                           CASE
                                               WHEN shape = 'VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro' THEN shape
                                               ELSE hardware_shape
                                             END 
                  ,
                           region) a) a)
GROUP BY region,
         ad,
         hardware_shape;

INSERT INTO compute.forecast_actuals SELECT b.pool_category10, b.pool_category20, b.pool_category30, a.month, region, ad, company_name, category, hardware_shape, shape, CASE WHEN company_name IN ('Cisco','DBaaS','FSS','Fusion Apps','GBU','LBaaS','Oracle Data Cloud','ODX-OKE','Oracle Labs','NetSuite','mPaaS','MpaaS','Ravello') AND pool_category10 = 'Usage' THEN company_name WHEN pool_category10 = 'Usage' THEN 'Organic' WHEN pool_category10 = 'Overhead' THEN 'OH' WHEN pool_category10 = 'Available' THEN 'HR' ELSE NULL END AS fc_customer_name, SUM(cores) AS cores FROM (SELECT TO_CHAR(record_date,'MON-YYYY') AS MONTH, a.region, a.ad, d.company_name, d.category, a.hardware_shape, a.shape, CASE WHEN a.server_type IN ('HV','SI') THEN 'VM' ELSE a.server_type END AS server_type, a.pool_name, b.capacity_state, b.capacity_category, b.super_category, SUM(a.cores) / 7 cores FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact a LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_state_dim b ON a.sub_state_key = b.sub_state_key LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compartment_dim c ON a.compartment_id = c.compartment_id LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.account_dim d ON c.tenant_id = d.tenant_id WHERE a.record_date IN (SELECT DAY FROM (SELECT DAY, MONTH, YEAR, day_of_month, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY YEAR,MONTH ORDER BY day_of_month DESC) r FROM dw_stg_user.date_dim a WHERE MONTH = TO_CHAR(SYSDATE -20,'MM') AND   YEAR = TO_CHAR(SYSDATE -20,'YYYY')) WHERE r < 8) GROUP BY TO_CHAR(record_date,'MON-YYYY'), a.region, a.ad, a.fault_domain, d.company_name, d.category, a.hardware_shape, a.shape, CASE WHEN a.server_type IN ('HV','SI') THEN 'VM' ELSE a.server_type END , a.pool_name, b.capacity_state, b.capacity_category, b.super_category) a INNER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_pool_dim b ON (LOWER (a.pool_name) = LOWER (b.pool_name) AND a.capacity_category = b.capacity_category AND a.super_category = b.super_category) GROUP BY b.pool_category10, b.pool_category20, b.pool_category30, a.month, region, ad, company_name, category, CASE WHEN company_name IN ('Cisco','DBaaS','FSS','Fusion Apps','GBU','LBaaS','Oracle Data Cloud','ODX-OKE','Oracle Labs','NetSuite','mPaaS','MpaaS','Ravello') AND pool_category10 = 'Usage' THEN company_name WHEN pool_category10 = 'Usage' THEN 'Organic' ELSE NULL END , hardware_shape, shape;

insert into forecast_data
(SELECT cf_date,
       CASE
         WHEN HW = 'Dense' THEN 'DenseIO'
         WHEN hw_generation = 'AMD' THEN 'AMD'
         ELSE HW
       END AS HW,
       CASE
         WHEN hw_generation = 'AMD' THEN 'X7'
         ELSE hw_generation
       END AS hw_generation,
       LOWER(cf_region) AS cf_region,
       fcst_type,
       customer_name,
       demand_type,
       fcst_version,
       comments,
       last_updated_on,
       last_updated_by,
       fc_customer_name,
       FC_MONTH,
       FCG_MONTH,
       fcg_month_start,
       SUM(cf_value) AS cf_value
FROM (SELECT *
      FROM (SELECT a.*,
                   CASE
                     WHEN fcst_type = 'Demand' AND demand_type = 'Organic' THEN 'Organic'
                     WHEN fcst_type = 'OH' THEN 'OH'
                     WHEN fcst_type = 'HR' THEN 'HR'
                     ELSE customer_name
                   END AS fc_customer_name,
                   TO_CHAR(cf_date,'MON-YYYY') AS FC_MONTH,
                   TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(REPLACE(fcst_version,' Forecast'),'MONTH yyyy'),'MON-YYYY') AS FCG_MONTH,
                   TO_DATE(REPLACE(fcst_version,' Forecast'),'MONTH yyyy') AS fcg_month_start
            FROM dw_stg_user.compute_forecast a
            WHERE comments LIKE '%Approved%')
      WHERE FCG_MONTH = TO_CHAR(SYSDATE -10,'MON-YYYY')) a
GROUP BY cf_date,
         CASE
           WHEN HW = 'Dense' THEN 'DenseIO'
           WHEN hw_generation = 'AMD' THEN 'AMD'
           ELSE HW
         END 
,
         CASE
           WHEN hw_generation = 'AMD' THEN 'X7'
           ELSE hw_generation
         END 
,
         LOWER(cf_region),
         fcst_type,
         customer_name,
         demand_type,
         fcst_version,
         comments,
         last_updated_on,
         last_updated_by,
         fc_customer_name,
         FC_MONTH,
         FCG_MONTH,
         fcg_month_start);

insert into forecast_limits 
SELECT  TRUNC(sysdate-2,'MM') a
       ,region, 
       CASE WHEN company_name IN ('Cisco','DBaaS','FSS','Fusion Apps','GBU','LBaaS','Oracle Data Cloud','ODX-OKE','Oracle Labs','NetSuite','mPaaS','MpaaS','Ravello') THEN company_name
       else 'Organic' end as fc_customer_name, 
       b.sku, 
       b.generation, 
       sum(limit_value*cores ) as limit_value_cores,
       to_char(TRUNC(sysdate-2,'MM'), 'MON-YYYY') as limit_month
        FROM dw_stg_user.limits a
        INNER JOIN compute.compute_shape_detail_dim b ON a.limit_label = b.shape       
        left outer join dw_stg_user.account_dim c on a.tenant_id = c.tenant_id 
        where group_name = 'compute'
        group by region, 
       CASE WHEN company_name IN ('Cisco','DBaaS','FSS','Fusion Apps','GBU','LBaaS','Oracle Data Cloud','ODX-OKE','Oracle Labs','NetSuite','mPaaS','MpaaS','Ravello') THEN company_name
       else 'Organic' end, 
       b.sku, 
       b.generation;

insert into forecast_prod WITH forecast_date AS ( SELECT TRUNC(TO_DATE(fc_month,'MON_YYYY'),'MM') AS fc_date, fc_month FROM (SELECT to_char(sysdate-10, 'MON-YYYY') AS fc_month FROM dual) ), data_forecast as ( SELECT cf_date as fcs_date, hw, hw_generation, cf_region, fcst_type, customer_name, demand_type, fcst_version, comments, last_updated_on, fc_customer_name, fc_month, fcg_month, fcg_month_start, cf_value FROM (SELECT * FROM (SELECT a.*, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY cf_date ORDER BY fcg_month_start DESC) -1 AS r FROM forecast_data a WHERE fcg_month_start <= (SELECT DISTINCT fcg_month_start FROM forecast_data WHERE fcg_month = (select fc_month from forecast_date))) WHERE (r = 1 AND   cf_date <(SELECT DISTINCT LAST_DAY(TO_DATE(fcg_month,'MON-YYYY')) +1 FROM forecast_data WHERE fcg_month = (select fc_month from forecast_date)) OR  FC_MONTH = 'JAN-2019') UNION ALL SELECT * FROM (SELECT a.*, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY fcg_month_start ORDER BY cf_date ASC) -1 AS r FROM forecast_data a WHERE fcg_month_start = (SELECT DISTINCT fcg_month_start FROM forecast_data WHERE fcg_month = (select fc_month from forecast_date))) WHERE r > 0) )     SELECT (select fc_month from forecast_date) AS forecast_version, a.*, CASE WHEN (select fc_month from forecast_date) = fc_month then '0' WHEN (select fc_date from forecast_date) > fcs_date then to_char((FLOOR(MONTHS_BETWEEN(fcs_date,(select fc_date from forecast_date)) / 6)*1)*6) WHEN (select fc_date from forecast_date) < fcs_date then to_char((FLOOR(MONTHS_BETWEEN(fcs_date,(select fc_date from forecast_date)) / 6) +1)*6) ELSE '0' END AS months_range FROM (SELECT a.*, b.cores, case when c.limit_value_cores is null then d.limit_value_cores else c.limit_value_cores end as limit_value_cores FROM (SELECT * FROM data_forecast ) a LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT usage_month, region, fc_customer_name, b.generation, b.sku, SUM(a.cores) cores FROM compute.forecast_actuals a LEFT OUTER JOIN compute.compute_shape_detail_dim b ON a.hardware_shape = b.shape GROUP BY usage_month, region, fc_customer_name, b.generation, b.sku) b ON (LOWER (a.fc_customer_name) = LOWER (b.fc_customer_name) AND a.cf_region = b.region AND a.hw = b.sku AND a.hw_generation = b.generation AND a.fc_month = b.usage_month) LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT region, sku, generation, fc_customer_name, limit_month, SUM(limit_value_cores) AS limit_value_cores FROM compute.forecast_limits GROUP BY region, sku, generation, fc_customer_name, limit_month) c ON (a.cf_region = c.region AND a.hw = c.sku AND a.hw_generation = c.generation AND LOWER (a.fc_customer_name) = LOWER (c.fc_customer_name) AND a.fc_month = c.limit_month) LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT region, sku, generation, fc_customer_name, limit_month, SUM(limit_value_cores) AS limit_value_cores FROM compute.forecast_limits where limit_month = (select fc_month from forecast_date) GROUP BY region, sku, generation, fc_customer_name, limit_month) d ON (a.cf_region = d.region AND a.hw = d.sku AND a.hw_generation = d.generation AND LOWER (a.fc_customer_name) = LOWER (d.fc_customer_name) )) a;

INSERT INTO free_tier_history
WITH dates AS
(
  SELECT TRUNC(SYSDATE -1) AS DAY FROM dual
)
SELECT *
FROM (SELECT a.*,
             pool_category10,
             pool_category20,
             pool_category30
      FROM (SELECT a.record_date,
                   b.instance_state,
                   b.capacity_state,
                   b.capacity_category,
                   b.super_category,
                   a.region,
                   a.ad,
                   UPPER(SUBSTR(a.ad,-4)) AS generic_ad,
                   a.pool_name,
                   a.shape,
                   a.hardware_shape,
                   a.server_type,
                   a.fault_domain,
                   a.serial_no,
                   common_name,
                   e.category,
                   SUM(a.cores) cores,
                   SUM(CASE WHEN a.server_type = 'VMI' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS instance_count
            FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact a
              LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_state_dim b ON a.sub_state_key = b.sub_state_key
              LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compartment_dim d ON a.compartment_id = d.compartment_id
              LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.account_dim e ON d.tenant_id = e.tenant_id
            WHERE a.record_date = (SELECT DAY FROM dates)
            GROUP BY a.record_date,
                     b.instance_state,
                     b.capacity_state,
                     b.capacity_category,
                     b.super_category,
                     a.region,
                     a.ad,
                     SUBSTR(a.ad,-4),
                     a.pool_name,
                     a.shape,
                     a.hardware_shape,
                     a.server_type,
                     a.fault_domain,
                     a.serial_no,
                     common_name,
                     e.category) a
        LEFT OUTER JOIN dw_stg_user.compute_pool_dim b
                     ON (COALESCE (LOWER (a.pool_name),'null_pools') = LOWER (b.pool_name)
                    AND a.capacity_category = b.capacity_category
                    AND a.super_category = b.super_category))
WHERE serial_no IN (SELECT serial_no
                    FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact
                    WHERE record_date = (SELECT DAY FROM dates)
                    AND   shape IN ('VM_STANDARD_E2_SUBCORE','VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro'));

insert into historical_burn_rate
WITH dte AS
(
  (SELECT MAX(record_date) as record_date
  FROM dw_stg_user.COMPUTE_CAPACITY_DAILY_COMPARTMENT_USAGE a
  WHERE record_date BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE -8) AND SYSDATE)
)
SELECT (select record_date+1 from dte) as record_date, hardware_shape,
       region,
       ad,
       SUM(hist_br_servers) AS hist_br_servers
FROM (SELECT a.*,
       (((cores - D1) +(D1 - D2) +(D2 - D3) +(D3 - D4) +(D4 - D5) +(D5 - D6) +(D6 - D7)) / 7) / cores_per_server AS hist_br_servers
FROM (SELECT a.*,
       LAG(cores,1,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D1,
       LAG(cores,2,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D2,
       LAG(cores,3,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) D3,
       LAG(cores,4,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D4,
       LAG(cores,5,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D5,
       LAG(cores,6,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D6,
       LAG(cores,7,0) OVER (PARTITION BY region,ad,hardware_shape ORDER BY record_date) AS D7
FROM (SELECT record_date,
             region,
             ad,
             case when a.shape = 'VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro' then a.shape else a.hardware_shape end as hardware_shape,
             cores_per_server,
             SUM(average) AS cores
      FROM dw_stg_user.COMPUTE_CAPACITY_DAILY_COMPARTMENT_USAGE a --used daily_compartment_usage to get average data for better accuracy 
        INNER JOIN compute.compute_shape_detail_dim c ON a.hardware_shape = c.shape
      WHERE record_date BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE -9) AND SYSDATE -- got back 8 days excluding current date
      GROUP BY region,
               ad,
               record_date,
               cores_per_server,
               case when a.shape = 'VM.Standard.E2.1.Micro' then a.shape else a.hardware_shape end ) a) a
where record_date = (select record_date from dte)
 )
GROUP BY hardware_shape,
         region,
         ad;

insert into inflight_data 
SELECT TRUNC(SYSDATE) AS record_date,
       region, ad, platform, hardware_shape, state, 1 as total, serial, servers_per_rack,
       CASE
         WHEN region IN ((SELECT DISTINCT region
                          FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact
                          WHERE record_date = TO_DATE(TO_CHAR((SYSDATE -1) -2 / 24,'DD-MON-YYYY HH24'),'DD-MON-YYYY HH24'))) THEN 1
         ELSE 0
       END AS cccp_region, delivery_date, provisioned_date
FROM (SELECT NVL(region,r1) AS region,
             NVL(a.ad,a) AS ad,
             a.platform,
             b.hardware_shape,
             a.state,
             a.serial,
             c.servers_per_rack,
             delivery_date,
             case when delivery_date+3<sysdate+1 then delivery_date+6 
                  else delivery_date+3
                  end as provisioned_date
      FROM (SELECT REGION AS r,
                   serial,
                   normalize_region(region) AS region,
                   region AS r1,
                   normalize_ad(normalize_region (region),ad) AS ad,
                   ad AS a,
                   platform,
                   CASE
                     WHEN state IN ('RECEIVED','INSTALLED') THEN 'LANDED'
                     ELSE state
                   END AS state,
                   CASE
                     WHEN state IN ('RECEIVED','INSTALLED','DELIVERED') THEN RECEIVED_Date
                     WHEN state = 'SHIPPED' THEN get_rack_delivery_date(serial)
                     ELSE NULL
                   END AS delivery_date, 
                   CONCAT(CONCAT (REGION,'-AD-'),SUBSTR(AD,-1)) AS "AD_CODE"
            FROM dw_stg_user.STOREKEEPER_MASTER_DB_STG a
            WHERE dw_dataset_date = (SELECT MAX(dw_dataset_date)
                                     FROM dw_stg_user.STOREKEEPER_MASTER_DB_STG)
            AND   region NOT IN ('R1')
            AND   OWNER = 'Compute'
            AND   TYPE = 'rack'
            AND   platform NOT LIKE '%Exa%'
            AND   state <> 'AVAILABLE'
            AND   SERIAL NOT IN (SELECT serial_no
                                 FROM dw_stg_user.compute_detail_fact
                                 WHERE record_date = TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE -2 / 24,'DD-MON-YYYY HH24'),'DD-MON-YYYY HH24'))) a
        LEFT OUTER JOIN compute.storekeeper_mapping b ON a.platform = b.platform
        LEFT OUTER JOIN compute.compute_shape_detail_dim c ON b.hardware_shape = c.shape) a;

insert into Accounts
    select  SYSDATE  as S_DATE , a.*  FROM dw_stg_user.Accounts a;

BEGIN
                FOR h in 0..0 LOOP
                    MERGE INTO COMPUTE_CAPACITY_TENANT_LEVEL_SUMMARY t
                    USING (
                        SELECT region, ad, admin_email, tenant_id, account_name, shape, record_date, instance_count
                          FROM compute_capacity_tenant_level_summary_v
                         WHERE record_date = TRUNC(sysdate-1) + (1/24)
                    ) v
                    ON (t.region = v.region AND
                        t.ad = v.ad AND
                        t.admin_email = v.admin_email AND
                        t.tenant_id = v.tenant_id AND
                        t.account_name = v.account_name AND
                        t.shape = v.shape AND
                        t.record_date = v.record_date)
                    WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET t.instance_count = v.instance_count
                    WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
                    INSERT (t.region, t.ad, t.admin_email, t.tenant_id, t.account_name, t.shape, t.record_date, t.instance_count)
                    VALUES (v.region, v.ad, v.admin_email, v.tenant_id, v.account_name, v.shape, v.record_date, v.instance_count);
                    COMMIT;
                END LOOP;
                DELETE FROM COMPUTE_CAPACITY_TENANT_LEVEL_SUMMARY
                 WHERE record_date < TRUNC(sysdate-7);
                COMMIT;
            END;
